#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/xor_sum.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/xor_sum.md:4
msgid "简介：`triton.language.xor_sum` 计算输入tensor沿指定轴的异或和，返回异或操作结果。"
msgstr "Introduction: `triton.language.xor_sum` computes the XOR sum of the input tensor along a specified axis and returns the result of the XOR operation."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/xor_sum.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.xor_sum(input, axis=None, keep_dims=False)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/xor_sum.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/xor_sum.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/xor_sum.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 说明 |\n"
"|--------|------|------|\n"
"| `input` | `Tensor` | 输入tensor |\n"
"| `axis` | `int` 或 `None` | 沿着哪个维度进行异或和操作。如果为None，则对所有维度进行异或操作 |\n"
"| `keep_dims` | `bool` | 如果为True，保持被操作的维度为长度1 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Description |\n"
"|----------------|------|-------------|\n"
"| `input` | `Tensor` | Input tensor |\n"
"| `axis` | `int` or `None` | The dimension along which to perform the XOR sum operation. If None, XOR is performed over all dimensions |\n"
"| `keep_dims` | `bool` | If True, the reduced dimensions are kept with length 1 |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/xor_sum.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`tensor`：输入tensor沿指定轴的异或和，返回异或操作结果\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`tensor`: The XOR sum of the input tensor along the specified axis, returning the result of the XOR operation.\n"

