#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/xor_sum.md:30
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/xor_sum.md:32
msgid "以下示例实现了对2Dshape的tensor进行xor_sum运算："
msgstr "The following example implements the xor_sum operation on a 2D shape tensor:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/xor_sum.md:34
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def triton_xorsum_2d(in_ptr0, out_ptr0, dim: tl.constexpr, M: tl.constexpr, N: tl.constexpr, MNUMEL: tl.constexpr,\n"
"                     NNUMEL: tl.constexpr):\n"
"    mblk_idx = tl.arange(0, MNUMEL)\n"
"    nblk_idx = tl.arange(0, NNUMEL)\n"
"    mmask = mblk_idx < M\n"
"    nmask = nblk_idx < N\n"
"    mask = (mmask[:, None]) & (nmask[None, :])\n"
"    idx = mblk_idx[:, None] * N + nblk_idx[None, :]\n"
"    x = tl.load(in_ptr0 + idx, mask=mask, other=-float('inf'))\n"
"    tmp4 = tl.xor_sum(x, axis=dim)\n"
"    if dim == 0:\n"
"        tl.store(out_ptr0 + tl.arange(0, N), tmp4, None)\n"
"    else:\n"
"        tl.store(out_ptr0 + tl.arange(0, M), tmp4, None)\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

